WEBVTT

00:06.481 --> 00:10.486
Marking the 20th anniversary of its devastating earthquake,...

00:12.235 --> 00:15.870
...ceremonies are being held in the Japanese city of Kobe...

00:16.039 --> 00:20.757
...to remember the almost 6500 people killed in the disaster.

00:23.296 --> 00:29.128
The city of 1.5 million was virtually destroyed in the 7.3 magnitude quake.

00:32.467 --> 00:38.421
Most of the victims died in collapsing homes or from fires that razed throughout the city.

